 r←{op}Diff y;rc;more;path;⎕TRAP;short;space;folder;buff;cmd
⍝ Returns a diff for all changes either...
⍝ * staged
⍝ * in the working area
⍝ * all changes
⍝ Option op-code "op" must be one of: "all" (default), "stage" or "work".
⍝ r is a matrix with two columns and zero or more rows.
⍝ `y` must be one of:
⍝   * Fully qualfied name of a namespace  that is an opened Cider project
⍝   * Fully qualified path to a Git-managed project
 ⎕TRAP←(811 'E' '⎕DMX.EM ⎕signal 811')(0 'N')
 op←{0<⎕NC ⍵:⍎⍵ ⋄ 'all'}'op'
 (space folder)←EstablishProject y
 cmd←'diff'
 :Select ⎕C op
 :Case 'stage'
     cmd,←' --staged'
 :Case 'work'
         ⍝ No action required
 :Case 'all'
     cmd,←' HEAD'
 :EndSelect
 (rc more r)←folder U.RunGitCommand cmd
 more U.Assert 0=rc
⍝Done
